		<outline text="Cryptocurrency" title="Cryptocurrency">
			<outline text="Bitcoin &amp; Crypto Trading: Ledger Cast" title="Bitcoin &amp; Crypto Trading: Ledger Cast" description="Ledger Cast covers the cryptocurrency industry (Bitcoin, Ethereum, and alt coins), including technical and trading analysis, fundamentals, and anything else crypto and blockchain related. Made by Ledger Status and friends." xmlUrl="https://feeds.simplecast.com/j5Cx9jps" type="rss" />
			<outline text="Bitcoin - The Currency of the Internet" title="Bitcoin - The Currency of the Internet" description="Bitcoin is the currency of the Internet: a distributed, worldwide, decentralized digital money. Unlike traditional currencies such as dollars, bitcoins are issued and managed without any central authority whatsoever: there is no government, company, or bank in charge of Bitcoin. As such, it is more resistant to wild inflation and corrupt banks. With Bitcoin, you can be your own bank." xmlUrl="https://www.reddit.com/r/Bitcoin/.rss" type="rss" />
			<outline text="Bitcoin Audible" title="Bitcoin Audible" description="The Best in Bitcoin, Ai, &amp; Development - Made Audible" xmlUrl="https://bitcoinaudible.com/feed/" type="rss" />
			<outline text="Bitcoin News" title="Bitcoin News" description="Daily Bitcoin News" xmlUrl="https://news.bitcoin.com/feed/" type="rss" />
			<outline text="BuyUcoin Talks - Medium" title="BuyUcoin Talks - Medium" description="BuyUcoin (https://www.buyucoin.com/) provides a simple and secure online platform for trading cryptocurrencies and blockchain-based digital assets. Users can profitably trade Bitcoin to INR, Ethereum to INR, and 150+ crypto to INR on a daily basis using EZ/OTC trade.buyucoin.com - Medium" xmlUrl="https://medium.com/feed/buyucoin-talks" type="rss" />
			<outline text="Cointelegraph.com News" title="Cointelegraph.com News" description="Cointelegraph covers fintech, blockchain and Bitcoin bringing you the latest crypto news and analyses on the future of money." xmlUrl="https://cointelegraph.com/rss" type="rss" />
