			<outline text="The Bitcoin Podcast" title="The Bitcoin Podcast" description="The Bitcoin Podcast is a show that discusses Bitcoin and Crypto topics in a laid back nature. From deep and technical topics, to laid back and philosophical topics...the gang, Demetrick, Corey and Jessie are just 3 guys looking to relax and talk about bitcoin. Established in 2015, one of the oldest crypto shows in the game." xmlUrl="https://feeds.simplecast.com/xCQr3ykc" type="rss" />
